OL,4,CGig workers promised rights crackdown
OL,5, The government has promised an overhaul
OL,6, of employment rights to improve
OL,7, conditions for millions of workers,
OL,8, including those in the gig economy.
OL,10,FThe changes include stricter
OL,11,Fenforcement of holiday and sick pay
OL,12,Frights, and higher fines for firms that
OL,13,Fbreach contracts or mistreat staff.
OL,15,FIt is a response to last year's Taylor
OL,16,FReview into working practices. 
OL,18,FBusiness Secretary Greg Clark said the
OL,19,Fmeasures would "address very clearly"
OL,20,Fthe rights of those in insecure work.
